HEADWORD: Hair-brown
<hw>Hair"-brown`</hw> <pr>(-broun`)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of a clear
tint of brown, resembling brown human hair. It is composed of equal
proportions of red and green.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

